text: The 1951 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy (USNA) during the 1951 college football season. Navy competed as an independent with no conference affiliation. The team was led by second-year head coach Eddie Erdelatz. ==Schedule== ==References== Navy Midshipmen Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Category:1951 in sports in Maryland
